      <title>१९९ धार्तराष्ट्र-मन्त्रणम्</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/mahAbhAratam/vyAsaH/goraxapura-pAThaH/hindy-anuvAdaH/01_Adiparva/14_vidurAgamanarAjyalambhaparva/01_dhArtarAShTra-mantraNam/199_dhArtarAShTra-mantraNam/</link>
